 ('5', 'field', '5', 'en_us', ' facing extreme and challenging conditions the goal of this month long expedition is to reach as many summits of the wolf s jaw massif as possible https www nationalgeographic com adventure destinations antarctica expedition antarctica expedition antarctica expedition antarctica storming castles conrad basecamp adapt 1900 1 coming soon after suffering dramatic setbacks in their lives three close friends who are among the world s best professional climbers battle their complicated pasts inner demons and nature s harshest elements in an attempt to confront the shark s fin on mount meru the most technically complicated and dangerous peak in the himalayas one that has never been scaled to completion http www merufilm com meru https itunes apple com us movie meru id1030748788 mt=6 ign itsct=1030748788 1030748788 ign itscg=0177 ign mpt=uo%3d4 20111101 meru 1386 compressed https www youtube com watch v=yvs6o9lvkkg leading the life of a climber involves a tremendous amount of sacrifice and hardship but for team athletes conrad anker and kris erickson there s no living without it https www thenorthface com about us expeditions always above us 2014 html always above us thompson hyaltite canyon conrad anker 1 https www youtube com watch v=xom6nktxof4 narrated by academy award winner robert redford national parks adventure takes audiences on the ultimate off trail adventure into the nation s awe inspiring great outdoors and untamed wilderness https nationalparksadventure com national parks adventure maxresdefault https www youtube com watch v=0iqf2tk_1wa '),
